data.meta_description: McGovern Medical School is the sixth largest medical school in the United States. Located in the heart of the Texas Medical Center, the school was established by the Texas Legislature in 1969 to address the shortages of physicians and the then-untapped resources for medical education in Houston.
data.meta_site_name: John P. and Kathrine G. McGovern Medical School at UTHealth
data.text:
UT Physicians has an updated website and finding the care you need is easier than ever before. As the clinical practice of McGovern Medical School, they offer primary and specialty care for the entire family.

Call 888-4UT-DOCS or use the online form to schedule your next appointment.
